            button.oh-button.button-default Default
            button.oh-button.button-green Green
            button.oh-button.button-red Red
            button.oh-button.button-blue Blue
            p
              | Do wanna bigger or smaller button? 
              | try the markup:
            :markdown
              ```html
              <button class="oh-button button-$SIZE">button text</button> // $SIZE in ['default','large','small','mini']
              ```
            p 
              button.oh-button.button-default.button-large Large button
            p
              button.oh-button.button-default Default button
            p
              button.oh-button.button-default.button-small Small button
            p
              button.oh-button.button-default.button-mini Mini button

            .explain
              :markdown
                Custom button color? use class `oh-button button-colorful COLOR` to customize

                We now support:
                ```html
                white white-bg
                gray gray-bg 
                light-purple light-purple-bg 
                yellow yellow-bg
                black black-bg
                blue blue-bg
                green green-bg
                orange orange-bg
                brown brown-bg
                pink pink-bg
                red red-bg
                light-green light-green-bg
                ```

              button.oh-button.button-colorful.red Red Ghost
              button.oh-button.button-colorful.light-green-bg Light green
              button.oh-button.button-colorful.brown-bg Brown
              button.oh-button.button-colorful.pink-bg Pink

