            h4.oh-h4.doc Dropdown
            | HTML markup:
            :markdown
              ```html
              <button class="dropdown oh-button button-default">Dropdown
                <div class="dropdown-sep"></div>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                  <li><a href="#">Item 1</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Item 2</a></li>
                </ul>
              </button>
              ```
